data.description: This sophisticated residence boasts four bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, as well as a loft and an office. On the upper level, you will discover a generously sized loft area, three guest rooms, a guest bathroom, a laundry room, and the primary bedroom, complete with a separate tub, shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. Our location is within the esteemed master community of Spencer's Crossing, which offers state-of-the-art sports parks, refreshing pools, engaging playgrounds for children, scenic walking trails, soccer fields, and basketball courts. It represents the ultimate family-oriented neighborhood where you can truly embrace the lifestyle you desire for your family. Come and experience the perfect harmony of living at Spencer's Crossing.
